Author: Alexithymia115
Text: Yup. I have an ivy league bachelor's degree in Neuroscience....... I had terrible anxiety yesterday eating a fried sweet potato. I went to bed convinced that I shouldn't try new food anymore. I'm still a bit convinced...

Author: godisamango
Text: Ya. I feel robbed of my own logic, and it sucks. Plus I get really dumb and forgetful when I low restrict.
